20 Article – State Government
21 9–1A–06.
22 (a) [The] EXCEPT AS PROVIDED IN § 10–14A–03 OF THIS ARTICLE, THE
23 following persons shall be licensed under this subtitle:
24 (1) a video lottery operator;
25 (2) a manufacturer;
26 (3) a person not licensed under item (1) or (2) of this subsection who
27 manages, operates, supplies, provides security for, or provides service, maintenance, or
28 repairs for video lottery terminals or table games; and
29 (4) a video lottery employee.
30 (c) (1) Except as provided in paragraph (2) of this subsection OR §
31 10–14A–03 OF THIS ARTICLE, unless an individual holds a valid license issued under this
32 subtitle, the individual may not be employed by a licensee as a video lottery employee.
33 9–1E–05.

